profile: For over 40 years, we have helped Ontario homeowners and builders build safer, more energy-efficient and sustainable communities. With a broad range of products and services, we are your insulation experts for existing home renovation upgrades and new residential home construction—satisfaction guaranteed. profile:
Serving Kingston, Brockville, Smiths Falls and surrounding areas.  Michael Rousseau WETT inspection has more than 30 years experience in the hearth products and wood-burning industry. Certified Master Technician/Master Sweep and SITE Comprehensive Inspection. 
Providing WETT Inspection reports to Insurance, Real Estate, and residential and commercial clients.  WETT is an acronym for Wood Energy Technical Training.  WET inspection, wet inspection, WETT certification, wett certification, are all terms for what is actually an inspection report on solid fuel burning appliances by a "WETT Certified" person - trained and certified to conduct these WETT Inspections and provide written and documented reports.
